<view class="container signature-page">
  <view class="page-header">
    <view class="page-title">手写签名</view>
    <view class="page-desc">点击进入全屏签名，完成后返回这里预览，再决定是否保存到相册。</view>
  </view>

  <view class="card preview-card">
    <view class="section-title no-bar">签名预览</view>

    <view wx:if="{{signatureTempFilePath}}" class="signature-preview-wrap">
      <image class="signature-preview" src="{{signatureTempFilePath}}" mode="aspectFit"></image>
      <view class="preview-tip">已生成透明背景 PNG，可继续重签或保存到相册。</view>
    </view>

    <view wx:else class="signature-empty">
      <view class="empty-mark">签</view>
      <view class="empty-title">还没有签名</view>
      <view class="empty-desc">进入全屏书写区后，可更流畅地完成签名，再返回当前页面确认结果。</view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="card action-card">
    <button class="btn btn-primary" bindtap="openSignatureEditor" hover-class="btn-hover">{{signatureTempFilePath ? '重新签名' : '开始签名'}}</button>
    <view class="btn-stack" wx:if="{{signatureTempFilePath}}">
      <button class="btn btn-secondary" bindtap="saveSignatureToAlbum" disabled="{{isSaving}}" hover-class="btn-hover">保存到相册</button>
      <button class="btn btn-secondary ghost-btn" bindtap="clearSignatureResult" hover-class="btn-hover">清空结果</button>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="notice notice-subtle tips-block">
    <view class="notice-title">使用提示</view>
    <view class="notice-row">签名过程会在全屏页完成，确认后只回传图片结果，不会自动保存到系统相册。</view>
    <view class="notice-row">如果需要重新写，只要再次点击“重新签名”即可覆盖当前结果。</view>
  </view>
</view>
